From: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
Subject: kABI: Hide change of header_ops.parse parameter change
Patch-mainline: Never, kABI workaround
References: CVE-2026-23451 bsc#1261604

Commit b7405dcf7385 ("bonding: prevent potential infinite loop in
 bond_header_parse()") adds a parameter to header_ops parse method.
Add the new version of parse as parse2 and take care of calling the
correct parse method.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
Reviewed-by: Jan Kara <jack@suse.cz>
